Banner Alzheimer's Institute NMRC Summaries

Source: R/data.R
BAINMRC.Rd

Banner Alzheimer's Institute NMRC Summaries data. More information is available at https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Usage

data(BAINMRC)

Format

A data frame with 2026 observations and 304 variables.

Source

https://adni.loni.usc.edu/data-samples/adni-data/

Details

  • ORIGPROT character Original study protocol , with options: ADNI1

  • RID numeric Range value: 2, ..., 1430

  • VISCODE character , with options: bl, m06, m12, m24, m36, m48, m60, m18

  • EXAMDATE Date: YYY-MM-DD
